article_title: TNA Wrestling referee Brian Hebner is pissed off about ‘stupid’ Obamacare – twitchy.com
article_text:
Looks like TNA Wrestling referee Brian Hebner is among the many Americans facing higher health insurance premiums under Obamacare. And he’s not happy about the “stupid” Obamacare idea.

https://twitter.com/babyhebner/status/418859588671528960

Hebner doesn’t do much tweeting about Obama, but he did fire off this election tweet in November.

https://twitter.com/babyhebner/status/265622851560808448
